title: many realizations ft. the ladygang

description:
Brooke and Danielle are back this week and joined by the LadyGang!  The gals discuss the difference between millennials and gen Z, friendship, relationships, and so much more.  Brooke and Danielle also share a mutual vent session as they both are coming to SO many realizations as the summer comes to an end.  Enjoy the episode and be sure to tag @galsonthegopodcast in your listening selfies and stories on Instagram!
